
* KDE   >= 4.2
* cmake >= 2.6.2
* optional: v4l or v4l2 enabled kernel
* libsndfile (development package or header for compilation, library for execution)
* libmp3lame (for mp3 encoding)
* libogg, libvorbisenc (for ogg/vorbis encoding)
* either ... a radio card, which is supported by your v4l/v4l2 kernel ;)
* ... or an internet connection and libffmpeg+libmms for internet radio streams
